### Test Scio.API Book Endpoints

# Get all books
GET http://localhost:5250/api/book HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

# Search books by title
GET http://localhost:5250/api/book/search?term=1984 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

# Search books by author
GET http://localhost:5250/api/book/search?term=orwell HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

# Add new book
POST http://localhost:5250/api/book HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pride and Prejudice",
  "author": "Jane Austen",
  "yearOfPublication": 1813,
  "isbn": "978-0486284736",
  "totalCopies": 4
}

###

# Borrow a book (replace with actual GUID from response above)
POST http://localhost:5250/api/book/{book-id}/borrow HTTP/1.1

###

# Return a book (replace with actual GUID)
POST http://localhost:5250/api/book/{book-id}/return HTTP/1.1

###

# Get specific book by ID (replace with actual GUID)
GET http://localhost:5250/api/book/{book-id} HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json
